{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "寻狗_叫花子斗嘴",
  "entry": "root",
  "meta": {
    "title": "寻狗Demo·①.5雾津街头·叫花子斗嘴（贫两句/走开·孤立flavor·对白待审）"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "root": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "小哥……行行好，赏两个钱，积个德嘛。",
      "next": "q",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "q": {
      "type": "choice",
      "promptLine": {
        "speaker": {
          "kind": "literal",
          "name": "旁白"
        },
        "text": "墙根蹲着个老叫花子，挂着个豁口破碗。"
      },
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "banter",
          "text": "〔凑过去贫两句〕",
          "next": "b1"
        },
        {
          "id": "grab",
          "text": "〔抢他半个饼〕",
          "next": "grab"
        },
        {
          "id": "leave",
          "text": "〔走开〕",
          "next": "leave"
        }
      ]
    },
    "grab": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "giveItem",
          "params": {
            "id": "banbing",
            "count": 1
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_叫花子斗嘴",
            "signal": "qiangbing_done"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "g1"
    },
    "g1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "关二狗一把夺过老叫花子手里那半个饼，撒腿就跑，跑出老远还听见后头在骂。",
      "next": "g2"
    },
    "g2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "遭雷劈的！抢老子的饼——你个背尸的不得好死！",
      "next": "end1",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "b1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "赏钱？老子比你还穷。你这破碗，还是我上回丢的呢。",
      "next": "b2",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "b2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "npc"
      },
      "text": "呸——你个背尸的，一身晦气比钱多。离远点儿。",
      "next": "b3",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "b3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "背尸咋个了？好歹是门手艺。你这要饭的，才是祖传的。",
      "next": "b4",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "b4": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "俩人你一句我一句斗了半天嘴，谁也没占着便宜，倒都乐呵。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "leave": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "关二狗摆摆手，绕开了。",
      "next": "end1"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    }
  }
